description: For sale: $499,900. Beautiful custom built home with over 3400 finished square feet.  Relax on the pretty wrap around front porch and enjoy all that this 10 acre country retreat has to offer.  Three spacious bedrooms...including a graciously sized master bedroom on the main level with a tray ceiling and private bath with separate tub and shower.  Vaulted ceilings, gas burning fireplace in the living room makes a statement in this open concept main level with a loft that overlooks the living room. Two stick built detached garage structures...one of them (30x40) is being used as a wood working shop with a livable space above with heat, kitchen and outdoor entry with a balcony. description: Recently sold: $750,000. Gorgeous one of a kind property on West Rush Lake and over 60 acres of beautiful land. There is a gas fireplace in the main living room and a wood burning fireplace in the lower level family room.  The two lower bedrooms are spacious and have extra large walk-in closets.  There is a Jack & Jill style full bathroom in the lower level where the tub/shower is on one side and the toilet is on the other with a sink in the middle for ease of sharing.  Spacious attached garage & the  30x40 pole shed has a cement floor & electricity.  Geo Thermal, beautiful views, wildlife right outside you window, master deck and lots of space to enjoy entertaining, fishing, lake living, acreage living and enjoying life.  Welcome Home!

Great way to make some $$ on your $$, & enjoy the privacy while you're at it.

The adjoining dining room has sliding patio doors that allow you to walkout to the 16x16 maintenance free deck that overlooks the backyard! The upper level has two bedrooms--one with a walk-in closet and a full bathroom! The recently finished lower level includes a ¾ bathroom with a tiled shower and a huge family room with a walkout to the patio! The massive outbuilding on this acreage property for sale in Stanchfield measures at  60x80 with concrete floors and 12x14 doors! 

Additional amenities of this beautiful Stanchfield acreage property for sale on 6.43 acres include: a new furnace in 2016, new water heater in 2013, new roof in 2011, insulated three car garage, quick access to Hwy 65, just a little over 10 minutes to Cambridge plus more! 

 **Bar in lower level not staying, washer/dryer included, refrigerator/stove will be switched out, will have fresh paint inmost rooms prior to close, swing set stays**
